TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, DIVISION_GROUP as DIVISION_GROUP, NVL(STYLE_NUM, '1' ) as STYLE_NUM, NVL(COLOR_CODE, '1' ) as COLOR_CODE, NVL(SIZE_CODE, '1' ) as SIZE_CODE, NVL(ATTRIBUTION_CODE, '1' ) as ATTRIBUTION_CODE, NVL(CUP_SIZE, '1' ) as CUP_SIZE, NVL(SKU, '1' ) as SKU, NVL(DIVISION_CODE, '1' ) as DIVISION_CODE, NVL(COMPANY_CODE, '1' ) as COMPANY_CODE, NVL(SAP_MATERIAL_NUM, '1' ) as SAP_MATERIAL_NUM, NVL(SAP_GRID_VALUE, '1' ) as SAP_GRID_VALUE FROM ( SELECT I.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP) as DIVISION_GROUP, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'slsp',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'slca',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'sli',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'hbi',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'exp',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM), 'mex',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'1') as STYLE_NUM,
DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'slca',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'sli',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'mex',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'1') as COLOR_CODE,
DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'slca',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'sli',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'mex',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'1') as SIZE_CODE,
DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slsp',TRIM(I.ATTRIBUTION_CODE), 'mex',TRIM(I.ATTRIBUTION_CODE),'1') as ATTRIBUTION_CODE,
DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slca',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'sli',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE), 'mex',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'1') as CUP_SIZE,
DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slu',TRIM(I.SKU),'sls',TRIM(I.SKU),'sld',TRIM(I.SKU), 'sli', RTRIM(SKU), '1') as SKU,
DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'sls','1', 'slsp', '1', 'sld', '1', 'slu',
'1','hbi','1','exp','1','mex','1', TRIM(I.DIVISION_CODE)) as DIVISION_CODE,
DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'sli',TRIM(COMPANY_CODE),'1') as COMPANY_CODE,
'1' as SAP_MATERIAL_NUM, '1' as SAP_GRID_VALUE FROM ITEM I WHERE LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')) AND I.ITEM_TYPE_CODE = 'SEL' AND I.ITEM_ID IN ( SELECT MIN(I.ITEM_ID) FROM ITEM I WHERE LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')) AND I.ITEM_TYPE_CODE = 'SEL' GROUP BY TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP) , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'slsp',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'slca',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'sli',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'hbi',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'exp',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM), 'mex',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'slca',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'sli',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'mex',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'slca',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'sli',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'mex',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slsp',TRIM(I.ATTRIBUTION_CODE),'mex',TRIM(I.ATTRIBUTION_CODE),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slca',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'sli',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'mex',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slu',TRIM(I.SKU),'sls',TRIM(I.SKU),'sld',TRIM(I.SKU), 'sli', RTRIM(SKU), '1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'sls','1', 'slsp', '1', 'sld', '1', 'slu', '1','hbi','1','exp','1', 'mex','1',TRIM(I.DIVISION_CODE)) , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'sli',TRIM(COMPANY_CODE),'1'), '1', '1' )
UNION ALL SELECT I.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP) as DIVISION_GROUP, '1' as STYLE_NUM, '1' as COLOR_CODE, '1' as SIZE_CODE, '1' as ATTRIBUTION_CODE, '1' as CUP_SIZE, '1' as SKU, '1' as DIVISION_CODE, '1' as COMPANY_CODE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slsp',SAP_MATERIAL_NUM, '1' ) as SAP_MATERIAL_NUM, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slsp',SAP_GRID_VALUE, '1' ) as SAP_GRID_VALUE FROM ITEM I WHERE LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')) AND LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = 'slsp' AND SAP_MATERIAL_NUM IS NOT NULL AND SAP_GRID_VALUE IS NOT NULL AND I.ITEM_TYPE_CODE = 'SEL' AND I.ITEM_ID IN ( SELECT MIN(I.ITEM_ID) FROM ITEM I WHERE LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')) AND LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = 'slsp' AND I.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM IS NOT NULL AND I.SAP_GRID_VALUE IS NOT NULL AND I.ITEM_TYPE_CODE = 'SEL' GROUP BY I.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM, I.SAP_GRID_VALUE) UNION ALL SELECT I.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP) as DIVISION_GROUP,
DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'slsp',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'slca',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'sli',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'hbi',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'exp',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM), 'mex',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'1') as STYLE_NUM,
DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'slca',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'sli',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'mex',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'1') as COLOR_CODE,
DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'slca',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'sli',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'mex',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'1') as SIZE_CODE,
DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slsp',TRIM(I.ATTRIBUTION_CODE),'mex',TRIM(I.ATTRIBUTION_CODE),'1') as ATTRIBUTION_CODE,
DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slca',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'sli',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'mex',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'1') as CUP_SIZE,
DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slu',TRIM(I.SKU),'sls',TRIM(I.SKU),'sld',TRIM(I.SKU), 'sli', RTRIM(SKU), '1') as SKU,
DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'sls','1', 'slsp', '1', 'sld', '1', 'slu', '1','hbi','1','exp','1','mex','1', TRIM(I.DIVISION_CODE)) as DIVISION_CODE,
DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'sli',TRIM(COMPANY_CODE),'1') as COMPANY_CODE,
'1' as SAP_MATERIAL_NUM, '1' as SAP_GRID_VALUE FROM ITEM I WHERE LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')) AND I.ITEM_TYPE_CODE = 'MFG' AND I.ITEM_ID IN ( SELECT MIN(I.ITEM_ID) FROM ITEM I WHERE LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')) AND I.ITEM_TYPE_CODE = 'MFG' AND LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = 'sli' GROUP BY TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP) , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'slsp',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'slca',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'sli',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'hbi',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'exp',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM), 'mex',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'slca',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'sli',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'mex',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'slca',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'sli',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'mex',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slsp',TRIM(I.ATTRIBUTION_CODE),'mex',TRIM(I.ATTRIBUTION_CODE),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slca',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'sli',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'mex',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slu',TRIM(I.SKU),'sls',TRIM(I.SKU),'sld',TRIM(I.SKU), 'sli', RTRIM(SKU), '1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'sls','1', 'slsp', '1', 'sld', '1', 'slu', '1','hbi','1','exp','1', 'mex','1',TRIM(I.DIVISION_CODE)) , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'sli',TRIM(COMPANY_CODE),'1'), '1', '1' ) ) ORDER BY ITEM_ID ASC --
